{"tid":501443,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇可能聖經唔係真相，但耶穌和耶和華是真實","createTime":"2017-12-16T20:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T08:18:55.000Z","uid":149978,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"562e483050e723b3304d467e987bb5d8f6431664","tid":501443,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T20:26:58.000Z","msg":"真實的超自然力量<br />\n<br />\n唔想透露一些野俾人類知，<br />\n但為左維隱，<br />\n只向少部分人顯然、行神蹟或超自然力量的表演，<br />\n所以創立此教。<br />\n<br />\n又或者，係一些超自然力量（神、鬼、靈魂、外星人等）為左在人類社會進行一些的實驗<br />\n<br />\n而創立此教，<br />\n所以部分人有宗教經驗或神蹟，<br />\n但多數沒有。"},{"pid":"eef2679bc68d3b781826b8ca17c7ac4550be5182","tid":501443,"uid":68802,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T20:31:10.000Z","msg":"我就係耶和華<br />\nD撚樣出本書作我d事跡你又睇得開心咪買囉"},{"pid":"6797e476a99f865f531a9fd652d2154c4b84b5b4","tid":501443,"uid":91664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T21:33:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我就係耶和華<br />\nD撚樣出本書作我d事跡你又睇得開心咪買囉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冒認"},{"pid":"080f596b58e283fbe3832592b86f78681b194aec","tid":501443,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T21:34:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae1dc9104616fde90cded049e8d23f2da7cdd0bf","tid":501443,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T21:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我就係耶和華<br />\nD撚樣出本書作我d事跡你又睇得開心咪買囉</blockquote><br />\n耶穌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca410268139ed6ac13e1ecfabb71667972ee7a94","tid":501443,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T21:41:39.000Z","msg":"夠鐘食藥"},{"pid":"1a68159442c474789fa2201d1f748d5ea69c91a4","tid":501443,"uid":14997